#: ../../source/administration/sunstone_gui/cloud_view.rst:15
msgid "How to Prepare the Templates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/sunstone_gui/cloud_view.rst:17
msgid ""
"When launching a new VM, users are required to select a Template. These "
"templates should be prepared by the cloud or vDC administrator. Make sure "
"that any Image or Network referenced by the Template can be also used by the"
" users. Read more about how to prepare resources for end users in the "
":ref:`Adding Content to Your Cloud <add_content>` guide."
msgstr ""

