#: ../../source/administration/sunstone_gui/cloud_view.rst:22
msgid "How to Enable"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/sunstone_gui/cloud_view.rst:24
msgid ""
"The cloud view is enabled by default for all users. If you want to disable "
"it, or enable just for certain groups, proceed to the :ref:`Sunstone Views "
"<suns_views>` documentation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/sunstone_gui/cloud_view.rst:26
msgid ""
"Any user can change the current view in the Sunstone settings. "
"Administrators can use this view without any problem if they find it easier "
"to manage their VMs."
msgstr ""
